data.title: BROCKPORT TAP ROOM
data.meta_description: Address: 4647 South Lake Rd Brockport, NY 14420 Phone: 585-431-0079 Hours: Sunday - Thursday: 11:00am to 10:00pm Friday Saturday: 11:00am to 12:00am General Man
data.text:
Hours:

Sunday - Thursday: 11:00am to 10:00pm

Friday & Saturday: 11:00am to 12:00am

General Manager:

Christopher Pickett

The Tap Room...

Is a Sports Bar, Grill & Billiard Hall connected to the restaurant. Stop in with family and friends for a game of Pool, Darts, or Shuffleboard. Watch the game on one of our 23 big screen high definition TV's. Enjoy Rochester's Best Burger and your favorite adult beverage!

What's on Tap...

We have a fantastic selection of Domestic, Imported, and locally brewed Craft Beer on Tap. Let us pour you a pint of your favorite brew or help you find a new favorite by trying a 4 beer flight!

Our selection of Craft Beer changes often...So check back to see what we have on tap for you!

Check us out on...

OR

Tap Here for a description of our draft beer selection!

Party Room:

Yes (Call to Book Your Event)

THE NFL SUNDAY TICKET...

Yup, We have that! Follow your favorite team every week on one of our 23 big screen TV's.
